Delegates attending the workshop believe the role of women has been compromised. The decried what they called persistent patriarchy in most media houses. They called on stakeholders to device ways and means that will see women given equal roles as their male counterparts in the media sector. The workshop is organized by the Egyptian Department of Foreign Ministry. Fatima Abbas-Hassan is the General Manager of the State-owned television channel, NTA, in Abuja, Nigeria...

--SABC--